-- New York Yankees Acquire Lance Berkman From Astros for Two Minor Leaguers
-- Jay Beberman
-- 2010-07-31T17:40:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-31/new-york-yankees-acquire-lance-berkman-from-astros-for-two-minor-leaguers.html

          
          
             The New York Yankees acquired Lance
Berkman from the Houston Astros for two minor leaguers.  
 Berkman, 34, will play first base and designated hitter for
the Yankees, the team said in a statement.  
          
          


  


        